text: Drumgoole is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *George Drumgoole Coleman (1795–1844), Irish architect *Jenny Drumgoole, American video artist *John Christopher Drumgoole (1816–1888), Irish American Roman Catholic priest *Noel Drumgoole (1931–1995), Irish hurler ==See also== *Drumgoole Plaza, a park in Manhattan, New York
